plot: The Librarians' first solo mission hits a snag when Baird loses the others in a mysterious Labyrinth that magically exists below the skyscraper of a modern corporation.

Baird is trying to train Ezekial, Cassandra and Jacob how to handle a (magical) situation should one arise. But all they want to do is go out on a mission. Baird doesn't think they are ready. But Jenkins reveals to them that the clipping book shows that 8 people have disappeared. They learn that they all were interns at a company. They go there and speak to the CEO and Baird suspects she knows more than she is saying. She goes to check on something while the others investigate on their own. They find themselves in what appears to be a maze complete with a Minotaur.—rcs0411@yahoo.com
